==English==

====Etymology====
From the Italian, from the Latin ''sabai'', (an Illyrian drink) + ''-one'', (an Italian suffix).

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''zabaglione'''
# A custard-like [[dessert]] made with [[egg]] [[yolk]]s, sugar and [[Marsala]] wine.

